    "Activities": "⚽🏀🏈⚾🥎🎾🏐🏉🥏🎱🪀🏓🏸🏒🥍🏏🪃🥅⛳🪁🏹🎣🤿🥊🥋🎽🛹🛼🛷⛸️🥌🎿⛷️🏂🪂🏋️🤼🤸🤺⛹️🏇🧘🏄🏊🤽🚣🧗🚵🚴🎮🕹️🎲🧩🎭🎨🎬🎤🎧🎼🎹🥁🪘🎷🎺🎸🪕🎻🪗🎯🎳🎰🎪",
